g\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫肥絲大隻解釋咪得囉！佢中文好叻咖嘛"},{"pid":"034dd5dba28ba9872dcb8d7283565e3134bd74fb","tid":575933,"uid":86988,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9fad636bef76ef8c4ce100f229428c6a772ac8b5","tid":575933,"uid":28583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋到點解讀「厲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"因為順口啲?<br />\n好似陳sir 黃sir嗰啲都唔會/好少讀正音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e47d811bd2ac07af85120b0282239377d00d68","tid":575933,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"034dd5dba28ba9872dcb8d7283565e3134bd74fb","tid":575933,"uid":86988,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9fad636bef76ef8c4ce100f229428c6a772ac8b5","tid":575933,"uid":28583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋到點解讀「厲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"因為順口啲?<br />\n好似陳sir 黃sir嗰啲都唔會/好少讀正音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"利是 = 勵事<br />\n真係咁多人唔知？"},{"pid":"97b67331743bd5ef087280cfc71a59d8c78e955c","tid":575933,"uid":81187,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"我唔知點解「利是」會讀做「厲是」，原因可能同個韻演化時嘅變化軌迹或方言接觸或音近以致出格有關，要留待高明解答。不過呢個唔係個別例子。<br />\n<br />\n「生熱痱」個「痱」（一作疿）一般都係讀 fai［苦委切］，但傳統字典音「fei匪」。<br />\n<br />\n又好似「砒霜」個「砒」，舊時字典其實係讀「pai批」，而家一般都係讀「pei披」。<br />\n<br />\n又好似「嚟」字，有讀「lai黎」，亦有讀「lei離」。<br />\n<br />\n又如果要追到去中古音，「翡」本應讀「fai廢」，但而家啲人都係讀「fei匪」。更甚者，古時「痱」、「翡」同音；「砒」、「批」同音。<br />\n<br />\n又例如「媲」「睥」古時同音，而家前者只讀 pei屁，後者字典pei、pai二讀皆有。<br />\n<br />\n當然咁唔代表 ai/ei 可以互換（例如利益、利潤就唔好讀厲益、厲潤，雪梨亦唔好讀雪黎啦），只係呢啲讀音可能係歷史痕跡，未必可以一刀切話錯。「利是」讀「厲是」既然唔係少數人嘅口誤，唔使覺得肯定有一個讀音係「錯」而要去「改正」。"},{"pid":"cf870bcfa8b23e85f02cfe173336144c7c8d290a","tid":575933,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"脷屎"},{"pid":"9d6ae661d01a2422a81d5957c67aac6b8950b050","tid":575933,"uid":169176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22da876dd96db54a6efa428225a947a73a7bcd74","tid":575933,"uid":61832,"like":3,"dislike":72,"score":-69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"紅包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"死翻強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24ba48e785642ece5ec03c5698ca328043968c5","tid":575933,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"瀨屎"},{"pid":"badbc7d704957a49357b23c710a9179bebf2b7a8","tid":575933,"uid":6275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老一輩嗰啲讀利是<br />\n00後嗰啲讀利是<br />\n而80 90後就會讀利是<br />\n不過外國人就鍾意讀<span style=\"color: red;\">pocket money</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed1342523b3f70dbf6b838462a785ff058d651e","tid":575933,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a4dc3f57073417b3fd935c69f10d9ec725b20b61","tid":575933,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"咁幾時開始出現利是呢樣野<br />\n當初點解會叫呢樣野做利是 而唔係叫紅包<br />\n紅包呢兩個字好易理解到點解會咁叫<br />\n但真係諗唔到點解會叫利是<br />\n一開始我以為係叫利事 祝大家新一年事事順利 但google下似乎利是先係正確"},{"pid":"5a496fc326550db9d6ff224bb721cac5af64f21c","tid":575933,"uid":133865,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:51:42.000Z","msg":"邊有人會讀厲時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多厲是姐"},{"pid":"f96707b60f97bb19eba4078bc31b023d279ce158","tid":575933,"uid":31173,"like":1